UID:MEbNYJypPdEHtmXMbXL8i
SUMMARY:CPR\\\, First Aid & HIV Certification
DTSTAMP:20260411T111857Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T190000
DESCRIPTION:Learn first aid\\\, infant\\\, child and adult CPR\\\, HIV and 
	bloodborne pathogens\\\, with a focus on injury prevention and safety. Mee
	ts L/I WISHA-WAC safety standards. Certificates issued at end of class. \\
	nCan you provide first aid in emergencies\\\, locate and take care of inju
	ries\\\, help a choking infant or child and stop cardiac arrest? Learn fir
	st aid\\\, infant\\\, child and adult CPR\\\, HIV and bloodborne pathogens
	\\\, with a focus on injury prevention and safety. \\nModified to meet COV
	ID-19 safety requirements (hands-on only\\\, no mouth-to mouth). \\nMeets 
	L/I WISHA-WAC safety standards. Certificates issued at end of class. \\nTa
	ught by Ken Norris\\\, Retired Firefighter. \\nLocation: Upper Blue Buildi
	ng\\\, Room 7.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/cpr-first-aid-hiv-ce
	rtification-2026-04/\n\nFrom Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/cpr-first-aid-hiv-certification-202
	6-04/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus\\\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\
	\\, 98103\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:phinney-neighborhood-association
CATEGORIES:Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:NogFofmB0y1j95H1_5hyt
SUMMARY:PNA Woodshop\\\, dedicated to Bill Fenimore
DTSTAMP:20260411T111857Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260508T180000
DESCRIPTION:Did you know that there is a woodshop in your area? Whether you
	’re a newcomer to woodworking or an experienced woodworker\\\, the PNA woo
	dshop is the ideal place to bring your creative projects to life. Whether 
	you’re interested in crafting a bench\\\, flower bed\\\, jewelry box\\\, c
	hair\\\, or cupboard\\\, the possibilities are endless. All you need to do
	 is become a PNA member\\\, attend an orientation\\\, and complete two saf
	ety classes. Once you’ve done that\\\, you can reserve your shop time and 
	get started on your project.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/pna-wo
	odshop-dedicated-to-bill-fenimore/2026-04-11/\n\nFrom Phinney Neighborhood
	 Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/pna-woodshop-dedicated-to-bill-feni
	more/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus: Brick (lower) Building\\\, 6532 Phinney Ave
	. N.\\\, Seattle\\\, 98103\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:phinney-neighborhood-association
CATEGORIES:Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
